{
  "stem": "3283.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So if a ballot showed a vote for the other guy, they put the X on it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it ruled out the ballot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The ballot was void.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's how he got elected.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, these things happen with politicians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The same as this guy D'Amato, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He's shrewd.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother volunteered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, he was an electrician.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was like, about 19 years old, but he learned to be an electrician.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he went overseas.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was in the engineering corps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he took charge of the lighting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, the searchlights, looking for planes in the sky.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember that, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then he came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then he started working for a photographer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, they used to put kids on the pony as they came out of school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he used to help-- and he used to photograph them, and that's how he learned photography.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then he went out for himself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he bought a little car, a replica of a Packard car.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he used to wait at the schools.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as the kids came out, he put them in the little car.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he went around with the proofs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he sold them, like a dozen for $10, and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then one summer when school was over, he asked me to join him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was going to go to Boston.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so I joined him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And believe it or not, we got to Belmont, Massachusetts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the from the school recess, the Kennedy kids-- John F.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Kennedy, Robert Kennedy, his sister, his older brother-- the one that died in the war--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "John.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Joe.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Joe.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, he was named after the father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We photographed all these kids.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Put some in the car.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
